testcase.name: If you add a file it should be a staged file
If you stage a file and then you modify his content it should be an updated file
If you stage a file and you don't modify his content it should be an non updated file
If you stage a file and then you modify his content v2 it should be an updated file
If you ask for general status it should return a list of files
If you commit a file and then you modify his content and add it it should be an staged file not yes commited
